{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_148", "text": "The browser verification is complete enough to document: the narrow viewport capture is clean, and I also extracted a tighter desktop crop from the workspace view because the full desktop route includes the surrounding multi-pane scaffolding and sticky rails. I\u2019m shutting down the temporary Vite server and then writing the required reviewer-facing summary file as the final step.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:58:21.940707-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "text": "The browser verification is complete enough to document: the narrow viewport capture is clean, and I also extracted a tighter desktop crop from the workspace view because the full desktop route includes the surrounding multi-pane scaffolding and sticky rails. I\u2019m shutting down the temporary Vite server and then writing the required reviewer-facing summary file as the final step.", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:58:21.940707-07:00"}
