{"event_type": "workspace.file_change_recorded", "event_version": "0.0", "file_changes": [{"path": ".yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/82_story_formatting_for_in_app_reading/summary.md"}], "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.file_change_recorded", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"changes": [{"kind": "add", "path": "/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/82_story_formatting_for_in_app_reading/summary.md"}], "id": "item_150", "status": "completed", "type": "file_change"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:59:40.825728-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:59:40.825728-07:00"}
{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_151", "text": "Implemented the reader-formatting pipeline end to end. The backend now owns deterministic manuscript formatting for chapter/heading/paragraph structure plus simple emphasis, DOCX export reuses that formatter, and the finalize reader now renders a typed reader document through a dedicated `StoryReader` component instead of reparsing raw text in React.\n\nVerification passed:\n- `pytest backend/tests/test_story_formatting.py backend/tests/test_story_export_service.py backend/tests/test_session_api.py -q` -> `51 passed`\n- `pytest backend/tests -q` -> `283 passed, 5 skipped`\n- `ruff check backend/app backend/tests` -> passed\n- `npm test -- --run src/features/session/StoryReader.test.tsx src/features/session/FinalizeStage.test.tsx` -> `5 passed`\n- `npm run lint` -> passed\n- `npm run build` -> passed\n\nBrowser QA was done with a local Vite server plus intercepted API responses because Docker was unavailable on this machine. Screenshots are at `/tmp/storyteller-finalize-reader-desktop.png`, `/tmp/storyteller-finalize-reader-mobile.png`, and the cleaner desktop crop `/tmp/storyteller-finalize-reader-desktop-readerbody-cleaner.png`.\n\nCode changes are committed at `a07c050` with message `feat(prompt-82): html markdown and reader formatting`. The required reviewer summary file is written at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/82_story_formatting_for_in_app_reading/summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:59:53.832558-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "text": "Implemented the reader-formatting pipeline end to end. The backend now owns deterministic manuscript formatting for chapter/heading/paragraph structure plus simple emphasis, DOCX export reuses that formatter, and the finalize reader now renders a typed reader document through a dedicated `StoryReader` component instead of reparsing raw text in React.\n\nVerification passed:\n- `pytest backend/tests/test_story_formatting.py backend/tests/test_story_export_service.py backend/tests/test_session_api.py -q` -> `51 passed`\n- `pytest backend/tests -q` -> `283 passed, 5 skipped`\n- `ruff check backend/app backend/tests` -> passed\n- `npm test -- --run src/features/session/StoryReader.test.tsx src/features/session/FinalizeStage.test.tsx` -> `5 passed`\n- `npm run lint` -> passed\n- `npm run build` -> passed\n\nBrowser QA was done with a local Vite server plus intercepted API responses because Docker was unavailable on this machine. Screenshots are at `/tmp/storyteller-finalize-reader-desktop.png`, `/tmp/storyteller-finalize-reader-mobile.png`, and the cleaner desktop crop `/tmp/storyteller-finalize-reader-desktop-readerbody-cleaner.png`.\n\nCode changes are committed at `a07c050` with message `feat(prompt-82): html markdown and reader formatting`. The required reviewer summary file is written at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/82_story_formatting_for_in_app_reading/summary.md).", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:59:53.832558-07:00"}
{"checklist_id": "item_42", "completed_count": 0, "event_type": "planner.checklist_recorded", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.checklist_recorded", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_42", "items": [{"completed": false, "text": "Add backend story formatting service, models, and DOCX integration"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Expose reader-document API and frontend typed client support"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Build StoryReader component and wire FinalizeStage to formatted output"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Run tests, browser QA, and write final summary file"}], "type": "todo_list"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:59:54.080612-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "tasks": [{"completed": false, "text": "Add backend story formatting service, models, and DOCX integration"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Expose reader-document API and frontend typed client support"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Build StoryReader component and wire FinalizeStage to formatted output"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Run tests, browser QA, and write final summary file"}], "timestamp": "2026-04-02T20:59:54.080612-07:00", "total_count": 4}
